article.headline: Netflix Inc. stock falls Thursday, underperforms market
article.body: Shares of Netflix Inc. NFLX, +1.43% slipped 0.54% to $531.79 Thursday, on what proved to be an all-around positive trading session for the stock market, with the S&P 500 Index SPX, +0.87% rising 0.80% to 3,446.83 and the Dow Jones Industrial Average DJIA, +0.56% rising 0.43% to 28,425.51. Netflix Inc. closed $43.58 below its 52-week high ($575.37), which the company achieved on July 13th. The stock underperformed when compared to some of its competitors Thursday, as Amazon.com Inc. AMZN, +3.01% fell 0.16% to $3,190.55, Walt Disney Co. DIS, +1.53% rose 0.15% to $123.09, and Comcast Corp. Cl A CMCSA, -0.99% rose 0.76% to $45.30.
